{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 248493, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 47252, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "旧家庭把人变鬼", "timestamp": 1597393608, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 248495, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 47252, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "幸福的家庭是相似的，不幸的家庭各有各的不幸", "timestamp": 1597393651, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 248498, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 47252, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : cz家庭条件不是特别好，但是就想待在家里", "timestamp": 1597393666, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 248504, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 47252, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "被压迫阶级的家庭本身就从制度上不太可能幸福", "timestamp": 1597393690, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 248510, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 47252, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz特别想回去，然而家庭条件自认为还不错", "timestamp": 1597393719, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 248511, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 47252, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一句旧家庭把人变鬼，真的是道出了靠封建礼教维持的所谓亲情背后的吃人逻辑", "timestamp": 1597393739, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 248519, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 47252, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 同意", "timestamp": 1597393809, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 248520, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 47252, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我也很想回去，并且自认为家庭条件不错。回学校没父母唠叨比较清净而已。建议dz少自作聪明。", "timestamp": 1597393808, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 248521, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 47252, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不同意，是否想回去和家庭条件没有必然联系，有可能只是单纯喜欢或不喜欢学校生活", "timestamp": 1597393832, "type": "text", "u